{{Weapon}}

== Overview ==
The Cyclic Laser design allows a faster cool down time for laser projectors, the design also offers a new dimension in damage infliction by increasing the firing rate beyond that of the [[Quad Argon Lasers|Quad Argon]] system. The downside to this high fire rate is a large energy usage.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Cyclic Laser can be bought in the workshop after acquiring [[Radial Laser Technology]].
